people: Sister Mary - Mrs. Harper & self - Mrs. J. B. Greenleafs - Mrs James Sergeant & Mrs Dr Elizabeth J. French
fullText: Sister Mary - Mrs. Harper & self took tea at Mrs. J. B. Greenleafs - with Mrs James Sergeant & Mrs Dr Elizabeth J. French - of Boston -
summaryText: Sister Mary, Mrs. Harper, and Susan B. Anthony had tea at Mrs. J. B. Greenleaf's with Mrs. James Sergeant and Mrs. Dr. Elizabeth J. French of Boston.
